@startuml Workflow Three Activity Diagram
title DormDash Workflow Three - Library Book Pickup & Return

start

:Student submits library return request;

:System creates service order;

:System retrieves all employees;

:Filter employees by shift availability;
:Filter employees by not busy;

:System selects best employee based on shortest travel time;

if (Employee available?) then (yes)

  :Assign employee to service delivery;

  partition "Employee Actions" {

    :Travel from employee dorm to student dorm;
    :Pick up library book at dorm;

    :Travel from student dorm to library;
    :Drop off book at library;

  }

  :System records service delivery;

  :Calculate ETA;

  :Send confirmation to student;

else (no)

  :No available employees;
  stop

endif

stop

@enduml